Honeymoon's over, Mrs. Evans.

26:24.533 --> 26:26.600
Oh, put me down
before you break your back

26:26.666 --> 26:28.766
Well, who asked you
to eat your way across Hawaii?

26:28.833 --> 26:31.966
Oh, what's the matter, lover,
you want skin and bones?

26:32.033 --> 26:34.000
Or you want voluptuous?

26:36.466 --> 26:39.300
Did I ever tell you
my sure cure for jet lag?

26:49.166 --> 26:51.100
This is the newly-wed game,
we're ready.

26:59.566 --> 27:01.633
If you say so, dad.

27:02.766 --> 27:04.800
What's wrong?

27:06.200 --> 27:07.966
